Plan 9 cannot rename across directories (wstat renames a leaf in place), and
std.fs.Dir.walk/deleteTree misbehave over 9P — move cache trees by recursive
copy+delete with entry names snapshotted before any delete. Covers both
Compilation.renameTmpIntoCache and Package.Fetch.renameTmpIntoCache (the
dependencies.zig move that zig build hits).

